            "title": "半日收市︱氣勢如虹 恒指漲598點報27725點 金融股領漲 芯片股再揚",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股昨天企穩兩萬七關口收市後，今早動力明顯提升，再創逾4年新高，金融、資源、科股等主要板塊攜手推高大市。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數早市全程報升，於初段出的的半日低位27258點時仍升131點，其後便呈一浪高於一浪的走勢，於上午約11時半衝上27786點高位，將升幅擴大至659點，刷新4年多的日中高位紀錄，尾市才略為回順。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指中午收報27725點，漲598點或2.21%。恒生科技指數升100點或1.74%，報5854點；國企指數升218點或2.37%，報9463點。主板半日成交增至1963.27億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指升655點，報27724點，低水1點。科指期貨升116點，報5854點，低水1點。國指期貨升233點，報9464點，高水不足1點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15618629-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e6%b0%a3%e5%8b%a2%e5%a6%82%e8%99%b9-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e6%bc%b2598%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b127725%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%91%e8%9e%8d%e8%82%a1%e9%a0%98%e6%bc%b2-%e8%8a%af",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-8.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 12:22:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
